author: Puidwen
title: A nice set unless you want a challenging build.
review: This set comes in a mixture of some large, and some very small parts.  A lot of small parts.  There are a lot of stickers in this set.  There is in fact only one print piece (not counting the minifig).  It goes together rather easily even with all the small parts.  When building i thought it was going to end up very blocky, but the finished project is actually very nice looking.  The minifig is a one print face, with legs.  She does however have a rather nice racing print on the torso.
